80
00:11:33,284 --> 00:11:34,175
Mom.

81
00:11:39,332 --> 00:11:40,883
- Woo-hee.
- Yes?

82
00:11:42,338 --> 00:11:44,354
- You shouldn't give up.
- Okay.

83
00:11:45,571 --> 00:11:47,854
