84
00:11:47,937 --> 00:11:50,044
- Let's try to improve your score.
- Okay.

85
00:11:50,127 --> 00:11:51,502
Okay, you can go.

86
00:11:51,585 --> 00:11:52,762
Thank you.

87
00:11:58,035 --> 00:11:59,125
Sit down, Yu-mi.

88
00:12:03,402 --> 00:12:05,162
I think

89
00:12:07,014 --> 00:12:10,074
you could get admitted to this school
even as a humanities major.

90
00:12:13,175 --> 00:12:16,119
