95
00:12:29,755 --> 00:12:33,175
Okay, I'll put my trust in you.

96
00:12:35,051 --> 00:12:38,897
Yu-mi,
your average is really good right now.

97
00:12:38,980 --> 00:12:40,935
You're missing the extra classes,

98
00:12:41,018 --> 00:12:44,704
but you can't let your marks drop
if you want to be an arts major.

99
00:12:44,787 --> 00:12:46,431
- You know that, right?
- Yes.

100
00:12:48,955 --> 00:12:49,976
Hi.

101
00:12:54,013 --> 00:12:55,831
Okay, you can go.

102
00:12:56,244 --> 00:12:59,216
My daughter received the top score
at her school.

103
00:12:59,299 --> 00:13:00,367
That's why.

104
00:13:01,123 --> 00:13:02,833
- Wow, the top score?
- Yes.

105
00:13:07,877 --> 00:13:09,290
What grade is she in?

106
00:13:09,373 --> 00:13:10,566
Her last year of high school.

107
00:13:11,189 --> 00:13:12,713
When she was this small,

108
00:13:12,796 --> 00:13:15,521
I made her coats and skirts myself.

109
00:13:15,604 --> 00:13:19,255
I run a tailor's down at that market.

110
00:13:20,844 --> 00:13:23,418
This is popular among kids these days.

111
00:13:24,007 --> 00:13:25,001
Yes.

112
00:13:25,831 --> 00:13:28,548
By the way, how much is that?

113
00:13:28,631 --> 00:13:30,033
- The price?
- Yes.

114
00:13:30,426 --> 00:13:31,879
We'll come back next time.

115
00:13:31,962 --> 00:13:34,113
- Dad, let's go.
- What's wrong? Don't you like them?

116
00:13:34,854 --> 00:13:36,609
- You said everyone wears them.
- Let's go.

117
00:13:37,303 --> 00:13:39,364
Should we check somewhere else?

118
00:13:39,447 --> 00:13:41,763
I thought about it,

119
00:13:41,846 --> 00:13:44,472
and I'm the happiest about my top score.
That's good enough for me.

120
00:13:45,293 --> 00:13:46,936
No, let's still go and--

121
00:13:47,019 --> 00:13:48,674
Dad, can you buy me a pork cutlet?

122
00:13:48,757 --> 00:13:51,391
I'll go to the academy after that.
Come on.

123
00:13:53,037 --> 00:13:55,532
Okay, let's go eat some pork cutlet.

124
00:13:55,932 --> 00:13:57,057
I'm hungry.

125
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,990
Let's hurry and eat some pork cutlet.

126
00:14:23,085 --> 00:14:24,040
Yu-mi.

127
00:14:25,460 --> 00:14:27,145
Must you go to an art college?

128
00:14:28,077 --> 00:14:31,167
Why do you want to paint?

129
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:34,130
Sir, please.

130
00:14:34,213 --> 00:14:35,737
