131
00:14:37,741 --> 00:14:39,551
Art is beautiful.

132
00:14:40,453 --> 00:14:42,086
I like beautiful things.

133
00:14:42,169 --> 00:14:45,597
No. No. That's vanity.

134
00:14:46,434 --> 00:14:48,200
Look at this painting.

135
00:14:48,283 --> 00:14:50,200
It's not beautiful at all.

136
00:14:50,283 --> 00:14:53,856
I'm asking because I'm anxious.
It's about getting accepted to a college.

137
00:14:55,285 --> 00:14:58,591
Your marks are good.
You should do what you're good at.

138
00:15:00,023 --> 00:15:01,635
Sir.

139
00:15:02,525 --> 00:15:04,656
I always do everything I put my mind to.

140
00:15:05,270 --> 00:15:06,584
