141
00:15:16,238 --> 00:15:18,932
ÉTRANGERE ATELIER

142
00:15:26,657 --> 00:15:27,726
How was class?

143
00:15:27,809 --> 00:15:28,764
Good.

144
00:15:29,534 --> 00:15:31,451
