145
00:15:32,272 --> 00:15:33,653
Really? Why is he always scolding you?

146
00:15:33,736 --> 00:15:34,916
- I don't know.
- What?

147
00:15:34,999 --> 00:15:36,250
- I don't know.
- You don't know?

148
00:15:37,560 --> 00:15:39,246
Finish it by next week, all right?

149
00:15:39,329 --> 00:15:40,945
Okay.

150
00:15:41,028 --> 00:15:42,655
There's always someone who's late.

151
00:15:42,738 --> 00:15:44,879
I'll see if you keep your promise.

152
00:15:44,962 --> 00:15:46,173
MEET ME IN THE STORAGE AT LUNCH

153
00:15:46,256 --> 00:15:49,077
