156
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:55,525
- Thank you.
- Good work.

157
00:15:59,132 --> 00:16:00,189
Hey, Yu-mi!

158
00:16:01,093 --> 00:16:03,463
- Where did she go?
- I don't know. She rushed off.

159
00:16:03,546 --> 00:16:04,680
Maybe she has to go really badly.

160
00:16:08,334 --> 00:16:10,102
- Wow! Sweet and sour pork?
- You're here.

161
00:16:10,185 --> 00:16:11,899
- Doesn't it look great?
- This is the best!

162
00:16:15,086 --> 00:16:16,233
Do you like sweet and sour pork?

163
00:16:16,704 --> 00:16:18,197
I love it.

164
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,346
Have your fill.

165
00:16:28,792 --> 00:16:30,169
Don't rush, eat it slowly.

166
00:16:53,719 --> 00:16:54,829
You should go in.

167
00:16:54,912 --> 00:16:57,396
- Call me when you get home.
- Okay.

168
00:17:04,625 --> 00:17:05,572
See you tomorrow.

169
00:17:06,451 --> 00:17:07,450
Bye.

170
00:17:14,855 --> 00:17:15,792
Bye.

171
00:17:16,784 --> 00:17:18,403
Hurry up and go home.

172
00:17:30,662 --> 00:17:32,543
Mom, I'm home.

173
00:17:33,153 --> 00:17:34,555
Since when?

174
00:17:35,195 --> 00:17:36,245
It's been three months.

175
00:17:36,328 --> 00:17:39,437
Why didn't you tell us?

176
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:42,357
And you've been getting top scores
while dating?

177
00:17:43,208 --> 00:17:45,200
- You're right.
- She's got it all.

178
00:17:45,283 --> 00:17:46,340
You're so lucky.

179
00:17:47,082 --> 00:17:49,061
Is it Son Jae-hyuk from Hongil High?

180
00:17:49,144 --> 00:17:50,999
He was always pestering you.

181
00:17:51,082 --> 00:17:53,263
- You're right.
- It must be him.

182
00:17:53,346 --> 00:17:55,328
- Is he handsome?
- I heard he is.

183
00:17:55,411 --> 00:17:56,473
