189
00:18:12,778 --> 00:18:14,930
I'm so jealous.
It's been three months already.

190
00:18:23,528 --> 00:18:24,761
Did you ask for me?

191
00:18:35,911 --> 00:18:36,935
Yu-mi.

192
00:18:39,543 --> 00:18:42,138
You must answer honestly to what I ask.

193
00:18:50,457 --> 00:18:52,786
Have you been dating your music teacher?

194
00:18:55,855 --> 00:18:57,563
Several people saw you,

195
00:18:58,345 --> 00:19:00,482
and he also confessed.

196
00:19:04,507 --> 00:19:07,354
It's common for students
to like their teachers.

197
00:19:10,055 --> 00:19:14,673
But the fact that
there was a physical relationship...

198
00:19:16,049 --> 00:19:17,163
That could be a problem.

199
00:19:21,175 --> 00:19:25,131
What do you mean?

200
00:19:25,214 --> 00:19:26,687
Hey, Yu-mi.

201
00:19:27,405 --> 00:19:31,267
Do you think you can get away with it
because your grades are good

202
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:35,504
despite your financial problems
and we've been nice to you?

203
00:19:36,215 --> 00:19:38,163
Sir.

204
00:19:38,246 --> 00:19:40,583
Talking to Yu-mi alone won't help.

205
00:19:42,547 --> 00:19:44,416
We need to bring her parents in--

206
00:19:44,499 --> 00:19:45,865
Her parents?

207
00:19:46,808 --> 00:19:48,259
Do they have any connections?

208
00:19:48,998 --> 00:19:50,492
Mr. Kim.

209
00:19:50,575 --> 00:19:53,795
There was an external report
to the police.

210
00:19:53,878 --> 00:19:55,705
We can't solve it on our own.

211
00:19:56,534 --> 00:20:00,090
We need to sort it out
before the school board and police come.

212
00:20:00,173 --> 00:20:02,842
Sir, I'm so sorry.

213
00:20:02,925 --> 00:20:05,147
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

214
00:20:05,230 --> 00:20:08,003
What a thing to do
at your first teaching job.

215
00:20:13,198 --> 00:20:17,204
I was only being nice to her.

216
00:20:17,849 --> 00:20:20,294
She approached me first.

217
00:20:20,377 --> 00:20:22,212
I should have declined. I'm sorry.

218
00:20:22,295 --> 00:20:24,009
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

219
00:20:24,092 --> 00:20:25,241
I'm sorry.

220
00:20:29,152 --> 00:20:30,415
What do you mean, approach?

221
00:20:33,637 --> 00:20:37,736
It wasn't like that.

222
00:20:38,805 --> 00:20:40,225
Why are you lying?

223
00:20:40,308 --> 00:20:41,406
Hey, watch it.

224
00:20:43,348 --> 00:20:44,492
Be quiet.

225
00:20:44,575 --> 00:20:47,184
Don't be cheeky
when the adults are talking.

226
00:20:49,374 --> 00:20:53,515
I'm sorry, Ms. Jung. I'm sorry, Sir.

227
00:21:01,930 --> 00:21:02,883
Attention.

228
00:21:03,747 --> 00:21:05,214
Bow to our teacher.

229
00:21:05,297 --> 00:21:06,987
Thank you.

230
00:21:26,602 --> 00:21:27,774
Hey, is it true?

231
00:21:27,857 --> 00:21:29,238
Why would you ask her that?

232
00:21:29,321 --> 00:21:30,958
We have to confirm.

233
00:21:31,041 --> 00:21:32,723
Still, don't ask things like that.

234
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:22,402
My sweet baby,
eat well and don't get sick.

235
00:22:27,803 --> 00:22:29,384
Take care of yourself.

236
00:22:45,245 --> 00:22:46,406
What about that jerk?

237
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,928
Why didn't he get fired?
Why only a suspension?

238
00:22:51,082 --> 00:22:54,205
Why must I run away
this early in the morning?

239
00:23:09,051 --> 00:23:12,704
