on the mock test last month,

248
00:23:36,096 --> 00:23:38,361
and she got the top score on her midterms.

249
00:23:40,902 --> 00:23:42,057
Okay, Sir. Please sit down.

250
00:23:42,140 --> 00:23:43,040
Okay.

251
00:23:43,123 --> 00:23:44,540
- Just a moment.
- Okay.

252
00:23:51,843 --> 00:23:53,008
Hello.

253
00:23:53,091 --> 00:23:56,302
Are you Ms. Jung Ha-na
at Hongjae Girls' High School?

254
00:23:56,385 --> 00:23:59,354
Hello.
I'm calling from Seowon Girls' High School

255
00:23:59,437 --> 00:24:01,181
