257
00:24:03,946 --> 00:24:07,191
that she was marked as a special student.

258
00:24:07,274 --> 00:24:10,978
Can you share what happened?

259
00:24:11,061 --> 00:24:12,113
Yes. Yes.

260
00:24:12,958 --> 00:24:14,113
Okay.

261
00:24:15,406 --> 00:24:18,377
Yes. Her scores are great, but...

262
00:24:21,781 --> 00:24:26,052
