00:24:38,608 --> 00:24:39,746
Come here.

266
00:24:48,767 --> 00:24:50,314
What's your average?

267
00:24:52,280 --> 00:24:53,347
A.

268
00:24:54,457 --> 00:24:55,756
What was your standing for the mock test?

269
00:24:56,881 --> 00:24:57,969
I was in the top five percent.

270
00:25:05,544 --> 00:25:08,326
Yu-mi, there are only four months.

271
00:25:09,096 --> 00:25:12,151
Don't try to make any friends
and just focus on studying.

272
00:25:12,898 --> 00:25:14,028
Understand?

273
00:25:14,769 --> 00:25:15,814
Okay.

274
00:25:19,554 --> 00:25:21,998
Sir, we need to talk.

275
00:25:22,081 --> 00:25:24,217
- Okay.
- Shall we go over there?

276
00:25:36,639 --> 00:25:38,717
