00:30:32,544 --> 00:30:33,564
Choi Yeon-ji.

321
00:30:36,465 --> 00:30:37,465
Lee Yu-mi.

322
00:30:41,208 --> 00:30:42,180
Kim Jung-mi.

323
00:30:45,841 --> 00:30:46,885
Song Min-ji.

324
00:30:50,810 --> 00:30:51,892
Jung Se-young.

325
00:30:54,535 --> 00:30:55,883
Jang Moon-ju.

326
00:30:57,520 --> 00:31:01,402
I'm sorry to inform you
that you have not been accepted.

327
00:31:01,485 --> 00:31:07,481
Examinee number 421723.

328
00:31:08,763 --> 00:31:12,265
I'm sorry to inform you
that you have not been accepted.

329
00:31:14,764 --> 00:31:18,916
Yu-mi, you have a call from Hongcheon.

330
00:31:30,759 --> 00:31:31,938
Hey, Dad.

331
00:31:32,021 --> 00:31:34,329
Why don't you ever call?

332
00:31:34,412 --> 00:31:35,833
Your mom's worried.

333
00:31:37,438 --> 00:31:39,889
I got a part-time job
since it's the break. I was busy.

334
00:31:42,094 --> 00:31:45,539
