335
00:31:45,622 --> 00:31:47,105
so I'm losing my regulars.

336
00:31:48,511 --> 00:31:49,620
How's Mom?

337
00:31:50,696 --> 00:31:51,945
How is she doing?

338
00:31:53,150 --> 00:31:56,657
Well... We went to the hospital yesterday.

339
00:31:57,326 --> 00:32:01,360
They say she's in her early stage
of dementia.

340
00:32:02,383 --> 00:32:03,329
What?

341
00:32:04,646 --> 00:32:06,755
Yes. Dementia.

342
00:32:08,391 --> 00:32:11,814
Will you come over one of these weekends?

343
00:32:17,289 --> 00:32:18,169
I'm sorry.

344
00:32:19,568 --> 00:32:20,634
It's okay.

345
00:32:22,047 --> 00:32:24,890
You don't have to come
if you don't want to see people.

346
00:32:25,766 --> 00:32:27,084
And...

347
00:32:28,631 --> 00:32:30,603
By the way,

348
00:32:32,481 --> 00:32:37,154
they didn't make
the admission announcement yet, right?

349
00:32:46,639 --> 00:32:48,155
I got admitted.

350
00:32:48,858 --> 00:32:49,809
You did?

351
00:32:50,689 --> 00:32:52,177
Well done, Yu-mi.

352
00:32:53,360 --> 00:32:56,529
Everyone asked, but we were worried
since you haven't called.

353
00:32:57,831 --> 00:32:59,244
Honey!

354
00:32:59,327 --> 00:33:01,682
Yu-mi says she made it!

355
00:33:02,279 --> 00:33:03,935
Why didn't you call right away?

356
00:33:04,018 --> 00:33:05,885
It's not that big of a deal.

357
00:33:05,968 --> 00:33:07,244
What are you saying?

358
00:33:08,136 --> 00:33:09,551
You did well.

359
00:33:11,647 --> 00:33:13,872
I'll call you back later.

360
00:33:16,541 --> 00:33:20,336
Congratulations, Yu-mi.

361
00:33:20,419 --> 00:33:22,255
You're always so quiet, so I didn't know.

362
00:33:22,338 --> 00:33:25,266
Tell me if there's anything
you want to eat. I'll make it.

363
00:33:27,672 --> 00:33:28,811
Gosh, it's cold.

364
00:33:42,024 --> 00:33:44,371
Dad. Dad, over here.

365
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:47,339
Yu-mi!

366
00:33:56,263 --> 00:33:57,702
The entrance ceremony ended already.

367
00:33:57,785 --> 00:33:59,526
Did we come too late?

368
00:33:59,609 --> 00:34:01,853
We were delayed
because your mom felt carsick.

369
00:34:01,936 --> 00:34:04,014
It's okay. There wasn't much to it.

370
00:34:04,097 --> 00:34:05,179
Did you get sick?

371
00:34:05,262 --> 00:34:07,877
I had to throw up at the rest stop.
I'm sorry.

372
00:34:10,405 --> 00:34:13,436
We wanted to tour around your school.

373
00:34:13,519 --> 00:34:15,264
There's nothing much. We can do it later.

374
00:34:15,347 --> 00:34:16,335
Here's a gift.

375
00:34:18,337 --> 00:34:20,725
Everyone has one of these things nowadays.

376
00:34:21,483 --> 00:34:22,411
But this is expensive...

377
00:34:22,494 --> 00:34:25,938
What are you saying?
I have to give the best to my daughter.

378
00:34:28,546 --> 00:34:29,671
We better take a picture.

379
00:34:30,246 --> 00:34:31,751
