00:34:53,654 --> 00:34:55,920
One, two, three.

388
00:35:00,972 --> 00:35:03,368
- Here you go.
- You shouldn't have.

389
00:35:03,451 --> 00:35:07,079
She got accepted thanks to you
who took a good care of her.

390
00:35:07,162 --> 00:35:08,731
I don't know how else to thank you.

391
00:35:08,814 --> 00:35:10,344
It was nothing.

392
00:35:10,427 --> 00:35:13,372
I was lucky to have a student
so well-behaved and quiet.

393
00:35:13,455 --> 00:35:14,998
- Really?
- Of course.

394
00:35:15,723 --> 00:35:17,673
Thank you for your kind words.

395
00:35:17,756 --> 00:35:18,823
No problem.

